query:
SELECT event_id AS event_id,
       substr(event_date::VARCHAR, 0, 11) AS "EventDate",
       health_worker_location_name AS health_worker_location_name,
       sms_type AS sms_type,
       anc_id AS anc_id,
       patient_name AS patient_name,
       age AS age,
       message AS message,
       logface_risk AS logface_risk,
       health_worker_name AS health_worker_name,
       event_date AS event_date,
       risk_level AS risk_level,
       location_id AS location_id,
       message_vietnamese AS message_vietnamese,
       client_type AS client_type,
       pregnancy_id AS pregnancy_id
FROM events_details
WHERE ((sms_type <> 'Newborn Report'
        AND client_type IN ('ec_woman',
                            'ec_family_member')))
ORDER BY event_date DESC
LIMIT 10000;
